<plot>Shady McGee, a young man forced to leave his bare apartment, unsure of what to do or where to go, is having a bad day that just couldn't get any worse. Carrying not even enough money to eat, he may be overcome with the temptation to steal. Meanwhile, a joyful jogger embarks on his daily jog to purchase a few items from the local market for his verbally abusive girlfriend. With a grin stretching from ear to ear, things just couldn't appear to be better for him. Comical mayhem ensues when these two strangers happen to cross paths.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?088178</url></doc>
